    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.abs(wp.cos(v1 + 0.75)))
    tmp = (0.68 + wp.cos(wp.abs(v0 + 0.14)))
    tmp = (0.53 / wp.sin(wp.exp(v1 + 0.36)))
    v1 = 0.96
    v1 = ((v0 + (v2 + 0.79 * tmp + 0.98)) / wp.abs((tmp + 0.41 / v1 + 0.63)))
    v0 = (0.03 / ((v0 + 0.86 * v0 + 0.86) * (v0 + 0.40 - tmp + 0.85)))
    v0 = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.90 * v0 + 0.95)) * wp.abs((v1 + 0.72 / v2 + 0.74)))
    v0 = wp.abs(((tmp + 0.56 - v1 + 0.70) - wp.sin(v2 + 0.65)))
    data[tid] = v0
